Project Overview
Kidosphere is a secure social media platform backend built with Django and Django REST Framework for kids and teens to share multimedia content, follow friends, send direct messages, and access curated educational and entertainment feeds.

Features
User registration and authentication (JWT tokens)

Profile management with extended user model (age, profile picture, bio)

Posting images, videos, and text content

Following/unfollowing users

Direct messaging

Curated educational and entertainment content feeds

Content moderation integration (OpenAI Moderation API planned)

Pagination and API filtering

Secure file uploads (local setup, extensible to cloud storage)